---
import BaseLayout from '../../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Criminal Defense Lawyer Marketing Malaysia | SEO & Lead Generation"
  description="Marketing strategies for criminal defense attorneys in Malaysia. Reach clients charged with crimes, DUI, drug offenses, and more."
>
  <article class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Marketing for Criminal Defense Lawyers in Malaysia</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        Criminal defense is urgent. When someone is arrested or charged, they need a lawyer fast. 
        Your marketing must capture these high-intent moments.
      </p>

      <h2>The Criminal Defense Client Journey</h2>
      <p>
        Unlike other practice areas, criminal defense clients often have immediate needs:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Emergency searches:</strong> "Lawyer for arrest" at 2am</li>
        <li><strong>Panic searches:</strong> "What happens if charged with [crime]"</li>
        <li><strong>Family searches:</strong> Parents/spouses searching for their loved one</li>
        <li><strong>Post-charge research:</strong> Looking for representation after initial court appearance</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>High-Intent Keywords to Target</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>"Criminal lawyer Malaysia"</li>
        <li>"DUI lawyer KL"</li>
        <li>"Drug possession lawyer"</li>
        <li>"White collar crime attorney"</li>
        <li>"Bail lawyer near me"</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Content That Converts</h2>
      <p>
        Educational content builds trust when potential clients are scared:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>What to do if you're arrested in Malaysia</li>
        <li>Understanding bail: Your rights explained</li>
        <li>Drug charges in Malaysia: Penalties and defenses</li>
        <li>Fraud charges: How to prepare your defense</li>
        <li>Juvenile criminal charges: A parent's guide</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Google Ads Strategy</h2>
      <p>
        Criminal defense is one of the most competitive legal advertising categories:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Bid on specific crime types, not just "criminal lawyer"</li>
        <li>Use location modifiers to reduce cost-per-click</li>
        <li>Run ads 24/7 – arrests happen anytime</li>
        <li>Mobile-first – most emergency searches are from phones</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Building Trust Online</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Case results:</strong> Win/acquittal rates (where ethically permitted)</li>
        <li><strong>Testimonials:</strong> Former clients willing to speak publicly</li>
        <li><strong>Media appearances:</strong> Commentary on high-profile cases</li>
        <li><strong>Credentials:</strong> Bar Council standing, years of experience</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Grow Your Criminal Defense Practice</h3>
        <p class="mb-4">We help criminal defense attorneys reach clients who need them most.</p>
        <a href="https://resultmarketing.asia" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">
          Get a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
